@node "4.0." "Can I use other than Aminet CD ROM's?"

 I  have no idea!  I guess as long as you make a tree file similar to the one
provided  and the CD is laid out the same or similar to Aminet then I see no
reason why you can't.  Try it.  Let me know the results.

@endnode

@node "4.1." "Can I help make this better?"

 Yes.   Firstly,  by  telling  me  it's  worth carrying on with this program.
Secondly, by pointing out any bugs you may find.  Thirdly, by offering ideas
that you'd like to see added.

@endnode

